/** Maybe a Material Mediawiki
/**
 * CONTENTS
 *
 * User configuration
 *
 * Global
 * Searchbox
 * Heimu (for https://moegirl.org)
 * Top
 * Main
 * Contents
 * Panel
 * Thumbimg
 * Gallery
 * Table
 * Navbox
 * WikiPlus
 * Hidden
